fields.Title of Contribution (if applicable): The Seasonal Newsletter of the Idaho Department of Fish and Game MK Nature Center
fields.Description/Abstract: By McCormick, M and Ziebarth, S. Guzzler Goes to Greener Pastures. In: The Seasonal Newsletter of the Idaho Department of Fish and Game MK Nature Center, Boise, Idaho. P. 7. The piece highlights the first field season of graduate research by my student Michael McCormick AND links to a website for a current collaborative project, ZyGoLife (http://zygolife.org/home/). The article is here at this Web Link: https://fishandgame.idaho.gov/public/docs/mkNatureCenter/newsletterFall2015.pdf
